item.title: Projects
item.description: Road Condition Analyser - India GitHub Repo URL: https://github.com/codesankalp/Indian-Road-Safety A step to ensure safe road journey. For more details read the README of the project. Developed using TensorFlow, Numpy, Open-CV, Django, Django Rest Framework, SQL as the database, Google Maps API, Dataset is provided by GRDDC 2020. Online Jupyter Notebook Developed Site URL: https://sankalp-notebook.herokuapp.com/ I made it for runnning my python code from anywhere. It is built using Docker and changing Jupyter config.
